{"tid":990703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【可憐怪羊】2頭3耳4眼睛 出生4日慘遭凍死","createTime":"2019-01-21T21:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T10:24:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"54ede863d94bae9310b290ac4c880ba98edc6f25","tid":990703,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T21:48:52.000Z","msg":"兩個頭、三隻耳、四隻眼睛，這不是外星人，也不是甚麼異獸，只是早前在安徽阜陽市一處牧場出生的一隻基因突變小羊！牠的奇怪外形曝光後，立即引起網民關注，就連英國小報《每日星報》（Daily Star）也有報道。可惜小羊在出生4天後，就因為當地氣候太過寒冷，而活活凍死。<br />\n牧場主人接受內地媒體訪問時表示，自己養羊十多年，從沒看過這樣的小羊。母羊在生產時難產，是他親自協助把小羊「拉出來」的。小羊生下來重約5公斤，但可惜天氣太過寒冷，沒幾天就死亡。<br />\n從網上曝光的影片可見，這隻基因突變的小羊有兩個頭、兩張嘴、三隻耳朵與四隻眼睛，但因為共用一條食道，兩張嘴無法同時進食。專家表示，像這樣的基因突變動物，大多都活不了多久。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190121/large/1548075865_1835.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190121%2Flarge%2F1548075865_1835.jpg&h=04126da5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190122/59168403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F59168403&d=Wqf%2BBtIb0uKZLQ16pRiKQTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=64d71db7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190122%2F59168403&h=7273ea80\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190122/59168403</a>"},{"pid":"b4d612ff05c9c2824c1cd88409f5e508781921a1","tid":990703,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T22:39:46.000Z","msg":"支那蝗婆遲早都生出一件咁既蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b99edbaadd7e576be44ceeca255e29b88f6995b","tid":990703,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:17:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9125b0edc2490be416da0b83d86a03a2d872125b","tid":990703,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4d612ff05c9c2824c1cd88409f5e508781921a1","tid":990703,"uid":47259,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T22:39:46.000Z","msg":"支那蝗婆遲早都生出一件咁既蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T10:24:05.000Z","msg":"應該即刻會被人攞去人道毀滅"}]}